\"color: red;\">vein</span> blood pressure呢？<br />\n實習個mentor raise呢個問題</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔係一定高過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未必掛<br />\nVein有muscle pump 又negative thoracic pressure draw blood返去<br />\n唔識</blockquote><br />\nSurely 高過vein<br />\n個pressure 係diminishing <br />\nCapillary -&gt;venule -&gt;vein-&gt;svc/ivc (the lowest)<br />\n因為 contraction force decreasing <br />\n利申 9 up</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5129245322a20f806d21292c1bbe1e16ab8471c3","tid":163930,"uid":4286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下epigenetics點改變得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不外乎CpG island, gene glycosylation, motif binding嗰啲啦"},{"pid":"f07f38cd5e3744be37a64baf8c9177a284df508b","tid":163930,"uid":454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"呢個po係咪仲係傾bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a3a69447870bdf4bfe51813a409f5065187695","tid":163930,"uid":4286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個po係咪仲係傾bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n博大精深啊  樓主又唔講明咩程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafd4a63a3ceeb6acfe3d93b0042a65630660177","tid":163930,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"Dependent 同independent 同controlled variables 分別係咩"},{"pid":"a1b6afd9acfbd261f2ff5b1627baa47c8a56af38","tid":163930,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dependent 同independent 同controlled variables 分別係咩</blockquote><br />\nDependent= 你要measure嘅嘢<br />\nIndependent = 你要轉嘅嘢<br />\nControlled = 你要keep constant嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n例如: 你要test肛交嗰陣1仔條j插幾入點影響0仔高潮嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndependent: 0仔要幾耐先高潮<br />\nindependent: 條j插入嘅深度<br />\ncontrolled: 抽插嘅frequency, temperature等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3871e7d14cc8150c33517142f60281b3290669f4","tid":163930,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個po係咪仲係傾bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n博大精深啊  樓主又唔講明咩程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實淨係識多dse level少少<br />\n學海無涯 回頭是岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f92bd99fae46d7651a4cf9d5932674fe852c44d","tid":163930,"uid":10164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:40:46.000Z","msg":"夜晚訓唔著<br />\n因為個身會發熱同埋好似手腳發麻咁<br />\n點解會咁 <br />\n<br />\n最後一樣落肚嘅野係9點幾嘅一杯咖啡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想訓"},{"pid":"8c95ea5f977ca4cc7a504c666d897c1932a60394","tid":163930,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T20:21:25.000Z","msg":"Dse level I guess <br />\n<br />\n你解唔解釋到ppl with Down syndrome 做mitotic cell division時候:<br />\n<br />\nAn extra 21st chromosome will line up with other two chromosomes to form one chromosome - homologous chromosome<br />\nll ll ll 21st<br />\n<br />\nOr<br />\n<br />\nAn extra chromosome will be left unpaired as a &quot;24th&quot; chromosome <br />\nll ll 21st - a pair of homologous chromosomes <br />\n..<br />\n<br />\nll &quot;24th&quot; chromosome left unpaired <br />\n<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"ac33bf82b346d18e5a09f08f3d081abef43f1e44","tid":163930,"uid":29929,"like":0,